data.description: WOW! Indulge in unparalleled quality, luxurious comfort, and a prestigious Glenmere address.  Step into this striking 2900+ sq ft. transitional floor plan that was built without comprise.Throughout, you'll find 9-foot ceilings accentuating the elegance of the space. The inviting owner's suite can be found on the first floor. The second floor boasts three generously sized bedrooms and an expansive versatile loft  perfect for your relaxation and entertainment needs. Looking for a home office? You've got it! This office space leads to the covered porch and an adjacent patio for your summer grilling activities. A charming rocking chair front porch, custom blinds, recessed lighting, and 42'' cabinets are among the many reasons to finalize your search for a new home. (Refrigerator, W/D do not convey) The corner lot offers extra parking for your guests.  Oh, did I mention this community has sidewalks, a swimming pool, dog park, and a walking trail?? And, Location, Location, Location!!!
